Package: basinbindr
Title: Catchment Delination for Germany
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Stoelzle", , "michael.stoelzle@hydro.uni-freiburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0021-4351"))
Description: With basinbindr you can delineate a catchment based on the location of gauging stations. The package uses the CATCHMENT-DE data set from the German Federal Institute of Hydrology (BfG) with around 400.000 basic catchments in Germany.
